\title{CREST Silver and Gold Awards (2021)}
\author{sebastianttaylor}

\p{These two awards were given to me in 2021 simultaneously for the project of "Building, Programming and Controlling a Quadcopter". I turned in a [37-page report](http://sttaylor.net/crest.pdf) on the project.}

\p{This was a naive 14/15 year old attempt at an integrated control system, and I refined the project after the award increasing the motor DAC resolution to 12 bits and the Python to C++.}
